com.riskgame.model

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.riskgame.model.Player

  • public class Player
extends java.util.Observable
    This class is a model stores the value associated to each player. It stores player's name of String type, total armyCount of player as Integer type, and the ArrayList of type Country which the player owns.
    Author:
    Shresthi Garg, Anusha
